 V45.15 (24.5.2005):   - further MOS specific optimizations
                       - improved version checks (OS 3.1)

 V45.14 (17.5.2005):   - MOS: stripped down to the very minimum:
                         no more HAM support, no more dithering,
                         24 bit output cannot be disabled
                       - MOS: highly optimized for MOS / V43 pic-dt
                       - Prefs: disabled all options that do not
                         have any effect under MOS
                       - Prefs: added new option "STRIPALPHA"
                         for disabling alpha output
